16
00:05:16,470 --> 00:05:17,930
It was a failure.

17
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:21,220
Someone had to be blamed, 
so it was you.

18
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,600
You like being a teacher?

19
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,520
I don't think I like you.

20
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:30,940
I just read your final report
on what happened to Discovery.

21
