29
00:05:55,250 --> 00:05:56,960
You think you could 
meet me halfway?

30
00:05:57,010 --> 00:05:58,090
Maybe.

31
00:05:58,590 --> 00:06:01,470
It doesn't take a very smart man
to appreciate...

32
00:06:01,930 --> 00:06:05,520
...the risk that I am taking
