33
00:06:06,470 --> 00:06:08,180
And you are a smart man.

34
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,810
This is a very bad business...

35
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,980
...in Central America.

36
00:06:15,270 --> 00:06:16,360
Very bad.

37
00:06:16,730 --> 00:06:21,450
Ships, other planes buzzing around
each other like angry hornets.

38
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:22,950
Very bad.

39
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:24,490
We didn't start it.

40
00:06:24,530 --> 00:06:27,370
We are scientists, you and I, Dr. FIoyd.

41
00:06:27,950 --> 00:06:30,040
