45
00:06:37,460 --> 00:06:40,590
-I don't have any time for games.
-This is a good game.

46
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,590
It's called '"The Truth.'"

47
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:47,010
For two minutes, I will tell only the truth.

48
00:06:47,810 --> 00:06:49,060
And so will you.

49
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,690
Two minutes?

50
00:06:50,850 --> 00:06:52,230
Two minutes.

51
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:53,940
Make it a minute and a half.

52
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:56,230
One minute and three quarters.

53
00:06:58,320 --> 00:06:59,400
You start.

54
00:07:00,450 --> 00:07:03,240
We know you are building
the Discovery Two...

55
