You're not familiar with the system.

85
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,960
And Ionger than that
to comprehend the data.

86
00:08:36,460 --> 00:08:37,710
I thought so.

87
00:08:38,290 --> 00:08:39,750
Thirty seconds.

88
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:42,460
Here we have our quandary.

89
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:45,760
We are going to get there first...

90
00:08:46,470 --> 00:08:50,010
...yet you have the knowledge
to make the trip work.

91
00:08:51,810 --> 00:08:53,850
How much more time do I have?

92
