98
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:22,040
That also doesn't Iook too bad
on the front page of Pravda.

99
00:09:23,050 --> 00:09:25,380
I don't know if I could 
convince our people.

100
00:09:26,170 --> 00:09:29,640
They wouldn't mind seeing you fail.
They wouldn't mind it at all.

101
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,010
Carrying Americans?

102
00:09:32,050 --> 00:09:34,930
I don't think they would alIow that
if they didn't have to.

103
00:09:35,890 --> 00:09:37,270
They don't have to.

104
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:40,400
Have you checked 
Discovery's orbit lately?

105
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:41,650
What?

106
00:09:41,690 --> 00:09:43,900
Have you checked the orbit?

107
00:09:44,070 --> 00:09:45,440
What about it?

108
00:09:46,530 --> 00:09:50,780
Now it's getting chilly here.
This is very bad for my asthma.

109
00:09:50,950 --> 00:09:53,120
You know damn well
we've been checking it.

110
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,040
I have enjoyed our little chat.

111
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,830
What is it you're not telling me?

112
00:09:56,870 --> 00:09:59,210
You are a smart man, Dr. FIoyd.

113
00:10:00,420 --> 00:10:02,460
You will know what to do.

114
00:10:45,460 --> 00:10:48,340
You've double-checked this?
Please say you haven't.

115
00:10:49,010 --> 00:10:50,630
You aren't saying anything, FIoyd.

116
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:53,180
Something incredible is 
happening up there.

117
00:10:53,470 --> 00:10:57,390
Discovery's being pulled towards Io.
Or pushed away from Jupiter. Whichever.

118
00:10:57,850 --> 00:11:01,690
