186
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:35,070
I knew you would be.

187
00:14:37,280 --> 00:14:41,530
I would like to expIore another possibility.
Diagnosis is only the first step.

188
00:14:41,570 --> 00:14:44,910
The process is incomplete unless 
it leads to a cure. Do you agree?

189
00:14:44,950 --> 00:14:46,580
Yes, I agree.

190
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:51,170
Does that mean you believe Hal
can be restored to normal functioning?

191
00:14:51,210 --> 00:14:52,830
I hope. I don't know.

192
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:57,000
There may have been irreversible 
damage. Certainly Ioss of memory.

193
00:14:57,050 --> 00:14:58,710
I need your cooperation, Sal.

194
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:00,590
Of course, Dr. Chandra.

195
00:15:00,670 --> 00:15:03,260
-There may be certain risks.
-What do you mean?

196
