We don't know from 100 beIow zero.

576
00:51:13,300 --> 00:51:16,140
-Raise the heat in his suit first.
-Yeah, I'm doing it.

577
00:51:16,180 --> 00:51:20,100
Shine your light on his face.
Make sure he doesn't turn blue.

578
00:51:20,350 --> 00:51:21,850
He's right in front of me.

579
00:51:22,150 --> 00:51:23,730
Keep talking all the time.

580
00:51:23,810 --> 00:51:27,030
All right, Leonov. 
I'm unsealing the visor.

581
