Hey, would I lie to you?

603
00:52:59,410 --> 00:53:01,450
HelIo, Discovery, are you there?

604
00:53:04,620 --> 00:53:07,830
Yeah, we're here. Everything's fine.

605
00:53:08,710 --> 00:53:10,630
