607
00:53:16,430 --> 00:53:17,840
You and me both.

608
00:53:20,010 --> 00:53:21,970
How do you say '"thank you'"?

609
00:53:25,730 --> 00:53:28,310
This is Milson, switching 
to KE-2 in five seconds.

610
00:53:28,360 --> 00:53:29,270
Mark.

611
00:53:29,440 --> 00:53:31,980
I wish I had better news.
It's getting worse here.

612
00:53:32,030 --> 00:53:34,780
