00:53:46,920 --> 00:53:49,170
I don't know if we're gonna 
be at war or not.

618
00:53:49,210 --> 00:53:52,420
It's terrifying hoping the Russians
are less crazy than we are...

619
00:53:52,460 --> 00:53:54,050
...when they are clearly crazy.

620
00:53:54,170 --> 00:53:56,630
Now I think you're in a safer place
