Continue. Yesterday.

662
00:56:56,150 --> 00:56:58,310
Tomorrow.

663
00:58:10,140 --> 00:58:12,510
Good morning, Dr. Chandra. 
This is Hal.

664
00:58:13,310 --> 00:58:14,930
